(581, '🔴 SUBMIT YOUR TRACK for the create together vol.5 month 🤝🦜', 'create together volume 5. month has started 🔴🕊️\nJoin the bitbird community for a month of creation,\nand a chance to have your track featured on the CTv5 Compilation!\n\nWhat can you expect from us?\nWe\'ll be extra present in the Discord server with weekly feedback. \nWe\'ll have guest appearances of artist sharing useful insights into their productions on YouTube. \nWe\'ll curate the final compilation from your submissions and release it as an official release. \n\nWhat do we expect of you?\nThat you have a good time, feel creative and free. \nWe want to encourage you to collaborate with people in the server, \nor find some people around you to collab with. \nThe motto for this month (and always) is create forever 🤝 create together.\n\nTO SUBMIT YOUR TRACK,\nUpload your track to Audius and tag it as a remix to this track\nPROTIP:  copy this track url before uploading\n\nfor more info check out\nhttps://www.audius.events/e/createtogether\nhttps://discord.gg/bitbird\nhttps://discord.gg/audius\n🦜', 711, 'https://discoveryprovider.audius.co/v1/tracks/ZZZq1WJ/stream'),
