(657, 'Pala Chrome ft. Jason Jeffreys - Mess You Made', '\'Mess You Made\' is something Jason Jeffreys and I have been sitting on for a hot minute, with the help of Jaydon Lewis on co-production and Shandy Sarantos on songwriting. Jason and I decided to work together on something completely new and different. We wanted to create a dark fusion of rock / grunge and industrial techno not having much of an idea of what the outcome would be. No need to say we are both pleasantly surprised with the result - Pala Chrome\n\nListen everywhere: https://bfan.link/mess-you-made\n\n-\n\nFollow Pala Chrome\nhttps://www.instagram.com/palachrome.mp3\nhttps://x.com/pala_chrome\n\nFollow Jason Jeffreys\nhttps://www.instagram.com/jasongrantjefferys\n\nFollow KUMO\nhttps://kumocollective.com\nhttps://www.instagram.com/kumocollective\nhttps://www.tiktok.com/@kumocollective', 804, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/k90zmzB/stream'),
