(921, 'trauma', 'This is a sad song for sad folks lol. It\'s uh...unfortunately based on some real sh!t. But hey, at least now we get to bang our heads to the memory of it haha...🙃 \n\nI\'d like to take this chance to not only say that I am beyond thrilled to take part in this contest, but also that I am so grateful for what bitbird has done for me and my perspective of music, let alone the world tbh. Back in 2016 when I heard Gouldian Finch 1, those tracks blew my mind and helped jumpstart my pursuit into music production, not to mention the impact that San\'s EP Victory had on me.(and honestly everything he\'s ever made since lol) I have been in love with bitbird from the day I first heard about this label. Thank you for being so awesome and thank you for setting up this contest. I am honored to upload my music alongside all these other talented people. I love you all, AND GOOD LUCK EVERYONE!<3 🦋\n\nFollow me elsewhere: https://linktr.ee/Monarchmusic', 1123, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/NR3BBx/stream'),
