(79, 'Person Online - Restart', 'next stop on our trip, a fresh restart from Person Online (previously known as Jonny Ha$h, Wiskers, and most recently Nytra - also, the founder of Night Owl Collective). after years of trial and error, it was time for one last hard reset.\n\nFeel Trip, Vol. 5: Eclipse is releasing one track at a time, Mondays Wednesdays and Fridays, Feb 16th - April 1st.\n\nfeaturing works from Zelgeon, Person Online, Schmoop, Mindex, Next To Blue, Innusta, Maynix, Echo Map, OSO, Vulpey, Glass Arrowhead, gHx, Blake Skowron, Vorso, COPYCATT, Seppa, Chalky, Herzeloyde, Keota, Shanic, Qynorah, Charlie W, and Hazia.\n&\nfeaturing art and visuals by tinyghost + mastering by Mindex.', 1089, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/79ldqB7/stream'),
