(91, 'Zelgeon - SLAPPP', 'kicking off Feel Trip, Vol. 5: Eclipse with a SLAPPP, Zelgeon returns with this absolute masterpiece of a tune! a perfect introduction to the journey that awaits, as we begin our descent into this 20-track compilation. Zelgeon, a Venezuelan based duo of identical twins, have so much talent oozing out of them, with such a beautifully unique mix of influences, it\'s such an honor to give this track a home and to be able to share it with all of you in our community and across the world!\n\nFeel Trip, Vol. 5: Eclipse is releasing one track at a time, Mondays Wednesdays and Fridays, Feb 16th - April 1st.\n\nfeaturing works from Zelgeon, Person Online, Schmoop, Mindex, Next To Blue, Innusta, Maynix, Echo Map, OSO, Vulpey, Glass Arrowhead, gHx, Blake Skowron, Vorso, COPYCATT, Seppa, Chalky, Herzeloyde, Keota, Shanic, Qynorah, Charlie W, and Hazia.\n&\nfeaturing art and visuals by tinyghost + mastering by Mindex', 1090, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/91WVxOO/stream'),
