(188, 'Dabow & Jon Casey - I Surrender', '‘I SURRENDER’ with @joncasey is OUT NOW on FMU Records!\n\nbig thank you to @alisonwonderland for getting us as first release\n❤️‍🔥✨📀🖤\n\nSTREAM: bit.ly/ISURRENDER', 225, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/XNvEpOR/stream'),
(189, 'Dabow x episcool x jordnmoody - Dale Vuelta', ' 🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢🎢\nDALE VUELTA OUT NOW ON JADU DALA\nhttps://jadudala.ffm.to/dalevuelta\nhttps://jadudala.ffm.to/dalevuelta\nhttps://jadudala.ffm.to/dalevuelta\n', 226, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/b6mKW/stream'),
