(232, 'Jaguar (Remy Heart Flip)', 'Flipped one of my favorite trap anthems.\nFREE DOWNLOAD: hypeddit.com/whatsonot/jaguarrhtflip\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic\nTW: www.twitter.com/remyheartmusic\nSpotify: open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i…lxS1O-MJ0DdbHsG', 278, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/E0QlVKQ/stream'),
(233, 'Impulse', 'Festival Remy Heart is back.\nFree Download:\nhypeddit.com/remyheart/impulse-dl\nStream:\nhttps://hypeddit.com/remyheart/impulse-stream\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic\nTW: www.twitter.com/remyheartmusic\nSpotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i7XiPNQTRoDxRr?si=2XAJMFlxS1O-MJ0DdbHsGA', 279, 'https://discoveryprovider.audius.co/v1/tracks/j4kz0xV/stream'),
(234, 'Don\'t Worry', 'New sound I\'ve been working on. \nHope you all enjoy it!', 280, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/v2vXvmp/stream'),
(235, 'Calvin Harris ft. Ellie Goulding - Miracle (Remy Heart Flip)', 'I fell in love with this song so I had to give it a proper trap flip/remix.\nI hope you guys enjoy it.\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic\nTW: twitter.com/remyheartmus\nSpotify: open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i…ypQK6sVo8XfShyvQ', 284, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/y70lMrr/stream'),
(236, 'Above & Beyond - Sun & Moon (Remy Heart Remix)', 'I recall listening to Sun & Moon for the very first time at EDC 2013. When those synths hit, it was a euphoric sound & feeling that rushed through my body. Ever since then I always wanted to remix this track.\nI kept the euphoric sensation of this track but flipped into a future bass/trap tune. I hope you guys enjoy this and that it gives you that same sensation I felt when I first listened to it.\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic\nTW: twitter.com/remyheartmus\nSpotify: open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i…ypQK6sVo8XfShyvQ', 285, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/Q6RGmBV/stream'),
(237, 'Paradiso', 'In paradise, there is only peace, prosperity, and happiness.\n\nStream: https://hypeddit.com/remyheart/paradiso\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic/\nTW: twitter.com/remyheartmusic\nSpotify: open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i…5VSFyb8blQXCw5oQ', 286, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/PgQaNN7/stream'),
(238, 'ELK, Chris Dogzout & UZ - Pressure ft. SoloSam [RH Remix]', 'Decided to finally release this unofficial UZ remix.\nHope you guys like it!\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic/\nTW: twitter.com/remyheartmusic\nSpotify: open.spotify.com/artist/05Bjrif4i…5VSFyb8blQXCw5oQ\n', 287, 'https://discoveryprovider.audius.co/v1/tracks/lW8GK/stream'),
(239, 'Fred Again. - Hannah (The Sun) [Remy Heart Remix]', 'I have been listening to this tune for the past 2 months non-stop.\nSo I had to remix it! Hope you enjoy it!\nDownload:\nhttps://hypeddit.com/remyheart/hannahremix', 289, 'https://discoveryprovider3.audius.co/v1/tracks/bbkYX/stream'),
(240, 'Calvin Harris ft. Kelis - Bounce (Remy Heart Remix)', 'Bounce was one of the first records that introduced me to dance music. I wanted to pay homage to this track by remixing it and adding my sound to it.\nHope you enjoy it!\n\nFree Download: https://hypeddit.com/nmn3ef\n\nFollow Me:\nIG: www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic/\nTW: twitter.com/remyheartmusic', 290, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/jzVQV/stream'),
(241, 'YTMH ', 'YTMH (You Take Me Higher)\nMy first DnB record I have ever released. \nMade this to capture the sound of underground rave culture. Hope you all enjoy it!\n\nStream it here: https://fanlink.to/ytmh\n\nFree Download: https://www.toneden.io/remyheartmusic/post/ytmh\n\nIG: https://www.instagram.com/remyheartmusic/\nTW: https://twitter.com/remyheartmusic', 291, 'https://discoveryprovider2.audius.co/v1/tracks/KvWMz/stream'),
