(275, 'Spira - The Unsent', 'More @spirasounds :\nlinktr.ee/spirasounds\n\nMore @recallrecords Heavy Dubstep :\nopen.spotify.com/playlist/2lZkawKMF0TFKoTSWdjScR\n\nlistentorecall.com\n\nThe Unsent, souls trapped on this plane, do not wish for you to proceed. To forge a path forward you must traverse a domain they are in full control of. Ice in your veins, you step forward.', 335, 'https://discoveryprovider.audius.co/v1/tracks/XBmNxEp/stream'),
