(495, 'Smoke Signals', 'When I wrote this track, I wanted to capture a similar feeling and vibe that CharlestheFirst used to bring in his music. RIP Legend.\n\nFollow me on Instagram, if you\'re into that sort of thing - www.instagram.com/trigomusic_/', 604, 'https://discoveryprovider.audius.co/v1/tracks/B0Pp6Oj/stream'),
